title: Trump Lauds FEMA Successes
description:
(4 Aug 2017) President Donald Trump visited the headquarters of the Federal Emergency Management Agency in Washingotn Friday.
Trump cited the rapid rebuliding of a bridge on Interstate 85 in Atlanta as a successful project managed by FEMA.
